assert ensure_value_object('hello') == [{'value': 'hello'}]
assert ensure_value_object([{'value': 'hello'}]) == [{'value': 'hello'}]
assert ensure_value_object([1, 2, 3]) == [{'value': [1, 2, 3]}]
assert ensure_value_object([[1, 2, 3]]) == [{'value': [[1, 2, 3]]}]
assert ensure_value_object({'hello': 'world'}) == [{'value': {'hello':
    'world'}}]
